   111	  CI jobs: `python-lint` (ruff), `python-typecheck` (pyright),
   112	  `python-test` (pytest).
   113	- **3b** — Schema ↔ model parity check. CI job `schema-parity` that
   114	  loads each JSON Schema and asserts the matching Pydantic model can
   115	  round-trip any instance; fails CI on drift.
   116	
